# Scripts Powershell

- Cmdlets basicos sobre procesos
```Powershell
ps | Sort cpu -Descending | Select name,cpu
ps | Select -First 5 | sort cpu -Descending
ps | select | group name
(ps | select Name).name | group
```
- Identificar un proceso nuevo
```Powershell
ps | select StartTime,name | sort StartTime
```
---------------

## Cmdlets
### Encontrar cmdlets
```Powershell
Get-Command -Noun Process
```

